sources.description:
Credit Card Conspiracy: When a Prank Turns Deadly...
A prank that starts with a group of college students creating a fictitious person so they can get a credit card develops into a plot that takes a murderous turn...

Original title: Paper Man (1971)
This film is subtitled in many languages. 
 
Director: Walter Grauman
Writer: James D. Buchanan
Stars:  Dean Stockwell, Stefanie Powers, James Stacy
Genres:  Drama, Mystery, Sci-Fi
